heading: Keyboard instrument ensembles.
general-note: Here are entered compositions not in a specific form or of a specific type for three or more different solo keyboard instruments or for unspecified keyboard instruments and collections of compositions in several forms or types for various numbers or combinations of solo keyboard instruments. Compositions for three or more of the same keyboard instrument and collections for various numbers of the same keyboard instrument are entered under. Piano ensembles, Harpsichord ensembles,. and similar headings..
When used for an accompanying ensemble in headings with medium of performance, the term "keyboard instrument ensemble" stands for two or more different keyboard instruments..
